# Cleanroom HVAC Calculator - Project Structure

## Main Entry Points

- Backend: backend/server.js - Express server
- Frontend: frontend/src/index.js - React app entry
- Database Init: backend/config/initDb.js - Database setup

## Backend Structure

```
backend/
├── config/
│   ├── database.js          # MySQL connection pool
│   └── initDb.js            # Database initialization
├── controllers/
│   ├── authController.js    # Authentication (login, register)
│   ├── customerController.js # Customer management (admin)
│   ├── projectController.js  # Project CRUD operations
│   └── standardController.js # Standards and classifications
├── middleware/
│   └── auth.js              # JWT authentication middleware
├── routes/
│   ├── auth.js              # /api/auth/* routes
│   ├── customers.js         # /api/customers/* routes
│   ├── projects.js          # /api/projects/* routes
│   └── standards.js         # /api/standards/* routes
├── services/
│   └── calculationService.js # HVAC calculation engine
├── .env                     # Environment variables
├── package.json
└── server.js               # Main server file
```

