## Database Tables

1. CUSTOMER - Customer profiles
2. LOGIN - Authentication credentials
3. ROOM_STANDARDS - 12 cleanroom standards
4. CLASSIFICATIONS - 68 classifications with ACPH
5. PROJECT - Project information
6. PROJECT_ZONE - Zone configurations
7. ZONE_ROOM - Room dimensions
8. PROJECT_ZONE_CALCULATIONS - Calculated HVAC values

## Key Configuration

- Backend Port: 5001 (configurable in .env)
- Frontend Port: 3000 (React default)
- Database: MySQL cleanroom_db
- Authentication: JWT tokens

## Important Files

- backend/.env - Database credentials
- backend/services/calculationService.js - HVAC formulas
- frontend/src/services/api.js - API integration
- docs/DESIGN.md - Complete system documentation
